functions.name: list

parameters.name: count
parameters.description: The number of elements to initialize the list with.

parameters.name: value
parameters.description: The value to initialize the elements with.

functions.description: Constructs the list with `count` copies of `value`.

functions.name: list

parameters.name: first
parameters.description: Iterator to the first element in the range.

parameters.name: last
parameters.description: Iterator to the element after the last element in the range.

functions.description: Constructs the list with the elements from the range [`first`, `last`).

functions.name: list

parameters.name: other
parameters.description: Another list to be used as a source to initialize this list.

functions.description: Copy constructor. Constructs the list as a copy of `other`.

functions.name: list

parameters.name: other
parameters.description: Another list to be used as a source to initialize this list.

functions.description: Move constructor. Constructs the list by moving the contents of `other`.

functions.name: push_back

parameters.name: value
parameters.description: The value to be added to the back of the list.

functions.description: Adds a new element at the end of the list, after its current last element.

functions.name: push_front

parameters.name: value
parameters.description: The value to be added to the front of the list.

functions.description: Adds a new element at the beginning of the list, before its current first element.

functions.name: pop_back
functions.description: Removes the last element of the list.

functions.name: pop_front
functions.description: Removes the first element of the list.

functions.name: begin
functions.description: Returns an iterator to the first element of the list.

functions.name: end
functions.description: Returns an iterator to the element following the last element of the list.

functions.name: size
functions.description: Returns the number of elements in the list.

functions.name: empty
functions.description: Checks if the list has no elements.
